transcript.text: SME Print Company reduces 60% of the order processing cost by offering Amazon like experience.
Research says 8 to 6% of customers says repeat sales depend on post purchase experience.
One of our customers has been an established print shop for 20 years.
Earlier his customers were placing print orders via walk in e-mail and phone.
One of the significant challenge was that one person was continuously busy answering customer calls to give order updates.
They were losing repeat customers as many clients were frustrated for not getting proactive updates.
Owner while ordering on Amazon realized that his customers were looking for a similar experience as he got an instant thank you e-mail and order update.
Suppose he could achieve Amazon experience which means happier customers and more repeat business on print shop.
Order management solution helped him achieve the same and now his team enters all orders into on print shop whether they get from e-mail, phone call, WhatsApp or walk in.
Solution auto sends job tickets with design file to the production team and auto sends order status, e-mail and SMS to customers.
As production team updates the same.
The client can track orders online and through my account sections can quickly reorder in the future.

On print shop Order management solution helped printer reduce 60% of the workforce needed to process orders and 90% reduction in the questions while customer places an order now easily offer Amazonlike experience without an IT team and at an affordable cost.
